<p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241202/1733140938765038004.png" title="1733140938765038004.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-12-02 200214.png" width="807" height="465" style="width: 807px; height: 465px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">回望那些逝去的时光，</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">无数个灯火通明的夜晚依旧清晰，</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">一页页厚重的篇章被你一一翻越，</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">一张张模拟的试卷记录了你的汗水。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">那些拼搏的日子，</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">已铸就成通往梦想彼岸的坚实桥梁！</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241202/1733141200506068265.jpg" title="1733141200506068265.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241202200449.jpg" width="802" height="695" style="width: 802px; height: 695px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">行至征途后半段，</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">疲惫常如影随形，暗暗缠上身来。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">可千万别忘了，</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">此刻，恰是最要紧的关头，</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">松不得一丝劲儿。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">每一回，退缩之意刚冒头，</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">就得在心底大喊，</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">曙光已在前方破云，</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">坚守才能拥抱辉煌。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">愿热血始终滚烫！</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241202/1733141320008016984.jpg" title="1733141320008016984.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241202200455.jpg" width="820" height="489" style="width: 820px; height: 489px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">清晨背诵　深夜复盘</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">看似波澜不惊的日复一日</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">一定会在未来某一天</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">让你看到努力的意义</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">希望日夜兼程逐梦而上的你</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">在考场上不畏考验不留遗憾</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">以笔为戎，以梦为马</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">或许会感到疲惫</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">或许会陷入迷茫</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">但请坚信</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">你的每一份付出都不会被辜负！</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">寻此苦旅，终抵繁星</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241202/1733141447388052074.jpg" title="1733141447388052074.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241202200502.jpg" width="849" height="608" style="width: 849px; height: 608px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">最后的冲刺阶段，</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">要迈着更笃定步伐前行。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">规划每日分秒，科学铺排复习，</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">把知识网织密，漏洞及时补全。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">别对难题犯怵，</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">要知艰难处，恰是蜕变机缘。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">身心俱疲之时，</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">不妨回望起点，</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">想想那个一直渴望实现的璀璨梦想</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">想想那个激情满满誓要达成梦想的自己！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">考研人，加油！</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241202/1733141525988061395.jpg" title="1733141525988061395.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241202200518.jpg" width="803" height="706" style="width: 803px; height: 706px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">考研征途</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">满是荆棘坎坷，</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">可你身旁总有温暖陪伴</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">研友并肩，</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">家人朋友托举，</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">更有逐梦不止的自己。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">待春至，花绽路旁，</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">前路亦满是芬芳。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241202/1733141632786089684.png" title="1733141632786089684.png" alt="微信图片_20241202200525.png" width="818" height="477" style="width: 818px; height: 477px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">希望在来年的春风中、暖阳中</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">花朵的盛开中</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">片片绿叶抽新枝中</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">每个人都可以</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">因为成功而热泪盈眶</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">每个人的奋斗努力坚持</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">都能得偿所愿</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">每个人都可以到达理想的彼岸</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">愿你</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">收获满满的喜悦与成功</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">一“研”为定！</span></p><p><br/></p>